data.title: Mead, Thomas (1841-1847)
data.meta_description: Mead, Thomas West Wycombe, Buckinghamshire (Thames Valley region); chair maker (fl.1841-1847) Listed at High St, West Wycombe (1841 Census); and at no address, West Wycombe (Pigot's Directory, 1844; Kelly's Directory, 1847). Thomas was 57 years of age in 1841.
